\id 2PE - Goofa 
\h 2 Phexiroosa 
\toc1 Phexiroosi Xaafida Nam77antho Kiitaa 
\toc2 2 Phexiroosa 
\toc3 2Phexi 
\mt1 Phexiroosi Xaafida 
\mt2 Nam77antho Kiitaa 
\imt1 Gaatha Qofaa 
\ip Hawaariya Phexiroosi xaafida nam77antho kiitay xaafettiday, dumma dumma bessan de7iya bini ammaniyaa asaassa. Ha kiitaa ayfe qofay, worddo asttamaareta iita oosuwanne entta timirttiya gaason medhettida yeellayaa de7uwa ixxana melassa. He medhettida metota digganaw oge gidanay, Yesuusa bantta ayfiyaan be7ida asatinne I tamaarssiya wode bantta haythan si7ida asati tamaarssida timirttiya baggara Xoossabaanne Godaa Yesuus Kiristtoosabaa ammanthiya eraa oykkanayssa. Xaafey minthidi odiday, “Kiristtoosi nam77antho yeenna” yaagiya worddo timirttiyabaa. He qofaa minthidi odishe, “Kiristtoosi simmidi yoonna gam77iday, asa ubbay ba nagaraappe simmana melappe attin oonikka dhayana mela koyonna gishossa” yaagees. 
\iot 2 Phexiroosa kiitaa ayfe qofata 
\io1 Sarotho \ior 1:1-2\ior* 
\io1 Ammaniya asaa xeessaa \ior 1:3-21\ior* 
\io1 Worddo asttamaareta \ior 2:1-22\ior* 
\io1 Kiristtoosa nam77antho yuussaa \ior 3:1-18\ior* 
\c 1  
\p  
\v 1 Yesuus Kiristtoosa hawaareynne iya aylley, taani, Simoon Phexiroosi, nu Xoossaanne nuna ashshiya Yesuus Kiristtoosa xillotethaa baggara nuyssa mela al77o ammano ekkidayssatas ha dabddaabbiya xaafas. 
\p  
\v 2 Xoossaanne nu Godaa Yesuusa eron aadho keehatethaynne saroy hinttew kumo. 
\s1 Xoossaa xeessanne dooruwa 
\p  
\v 3 Ba bonchchoninne lo77otethan nuna xeegida iya eron de7osinne Xoossaa daanidi daanaw koshshiyaba ubbaa Xoossay ba wolqqan nuus immis.  
\v 4 Hintte iita amo gaason medhettiya ha alamiyan de7iya bashshaafe kessi ekkanaadanne Xoossaa xoossatethan shaakettanaada, ha imotata baggara daro al77onne gita ufayssaa nuus immis.  
\v 5 Hessa gisho, minnidi, hintte ammanuwa bolla lo77otethi, lo77otetha bolla eratethi,  
\v 6 eratetha bolla bana haaro, bana haaro bolla gencca, gencca bolla Xoossaa daano,  
\v 7 Xoossaa daano bolla ishatetha keehatethi, ishatetha keehatetha bolla siiqo gujjite.  
\v 8 Hayssati hinttew daridi de7iyabaa gidikko, Godaa Yesuus Kiristtoosa eron maaddiya asinne ayfera de7iya asi oothana.  
\v 9 Shin hessati baynna oonikka matan de7iyabaa xalaala be7iya qooqe. I ba kase nagaraappe geeyidayssa dogis. 
\p  
\v 10 Hessa gisho, ta ishato, hintte xeessanne hintte dooruwa minthanaw kaseyssafe aathidi minnite. Hintte hessata oothiyabaa gidikko, dhubetteketa.  
\v 11 Hessan nu Godaanne nuna ashshiya Yesuus Kiristtoosa merinaa kawotethaa geliya kumetha maatay hinttew imettana. 
\p  
\v 12 Hessa gisho, hintte hayssata eriyabaanne he oykkida tuman minnidi de7iyabaa gidikkoka, taani hayssata ubba wode hinttena hassayiso aggike.  
\v 13 Taani shemppora de7ida wode ubban hinttena hassayisanayssi koshshiyabaa gada qoppays.  
\v 14 Nu Godaa Yesuus Kiristtoosi taw qonccisadayssada taani ha hayqqiya asatethaa gam77onna qaara yeggada baanayssa erays.  
\v 15 Taani hinttefe shaakettikokka hintte hayssata ubba wode akeekana mela taw dandda7ettiyabaa ubbaa oothana. 
\p  
\v 16 Nuuni Godaa Kiristtoosa wolqqaanne iya yuussabaa hinttew odey, iya gita bonchchuwa be7idippe attin medhdhi kessida hayse gidenna.  
\v 17 Daro wolqqaama bonchchuwafe, “Taani ufayttiya, ta dosiya na7ay hayssa” yaagiya qaalay yida wode Xoossaa Aawappe bonchchonne galata ekkis.\x - \xo 1:17 \xt Maato 17:1-5; Mar 9:2-7; Luuqa 9:28-35\x* 
\v 18 Nuuni geeshsha deriya bolla iyara de7iya wode he qaalay saloppe yishin si7ida. 
\p  
\v 19 Nuus hessafe aadhdhiya ammanettida tinbbite qaali de7ees. Sa7i wonttana gakkanawunne bakkali hintte wozanan dolana gakkanaw, dhuman poo7iya poo7o asi naageyssada, hintte he qaalaa naagikko lo77o ootheeta.  
\v 20 Ubbaafe kasetidi hayssa erite. Geeshsha Maxaafan xaafettida tinbbite qaala oonikka ba dosidaada birshshanaw dandda7enna.  
\v 21 Tinbbite ubbaa, Xoossay kiittida asati Geeshsha Ayyaanay kaalethin, odidosonappe attin asa shenen odibookkona. 
\c 2  
\s1 Worddo asttamaareta 
\p  
\v 1 Shin worddo nabeti kase asaa giddon de7eyssa mela ha77ika worddo asttamaareti hintte giddon denddana. Entti banttana wozida, Godaa kaddidi, dhayssiya worddo timirttiya ehana. Hessan entti bantta bolla ellesidi dhayo ehoosona.  
\v 2 Daro asay yeellayaa entta iita ogiya kaallana; entta gaason tuma ogey cayettana.  
\v 3 Worddo asttamaareti miishe yaaridi banttaw medhdhi kessida hayssen hinttena bonqana. Benippe doomidi entta pirdday giigi uttis; entta dhayoykka enttana naagi uttis. 
\p  
\v 4 Nagara oothida kiitanchchotas Xoossay qadhettonna, pirdda gallas gakkanaw gaanname dhuma ollan entta qachchi yeggis.  
\v 5 Hessadakka, Xoossay xillotethabaa odiya Nohenne hara laappun asata ashshidi, Xoossaa goynnona asay de7iya beni alamiya qadhettonna dhayo haathan dhayssis.\x - \xo 2:5 \xt Medhe 6:1-7:24\x* 
\v 6 Geellatas leemiso gidana mela Xoossay Soodomenne Gamoora katamata bido oothidi xuuggidi dhayssis.\x - \xo 2:6 \xt Medhe 19:24\x* 
\v 7 Higges kiitettonna laymatiya asata giddon waayettishe de7ida xillo Looxe Xoossay ashshis.\x - \xo 2:7 \xt Medhe 19:1-16\x* 
\v 8 He xillo addey entta giddon de7ishe, entti oothiya iita oosuwa gallas gallas be7ida wodenne si7ida wode iya lo77o wozanay un77ettees.  
\v 9 Hessa gidikko, Goday, bana goynniya asata paaceppe waati ashshaneekko, qassi nagaranchchota pirdda gallasaas gakkanaw waattidi seerishe naagisaneekko erees.  
\v 10 Ubbaafe aathidi tuna amon asho qofa kaalleyssatanne maata aawata kadheyssata, pirdda gallas gakkanaw Goday naagisis. 
\p He asati ganjje minonne otoranchcho gidiya gisho salo medhetethata cayishe yayyokonna.  
\v 11 Shin kiitanchchoti worddo asttamaaretappe wolqqaninne minotethan daro aadhdhoosonashin Godaa sinthan salo medhetethata cayokkona.  
\v 12 Shin he asati bantta eronnaban gelidi cayoosona. Entti oykettanawnne hayqqanaw yelettida, wozani baynna do7a mela hanoosona; enttika wora do7ada coo dhayana. 
\p  
\v 13 Entti gathida metuwada zaari metootana. Seeta gallas yexxishe guppeyssa ufayssiyabaa gidi qoppoosona. Entti kawushshatanne tunata gidi de7ishe hinttera shaakettiya siiqo imatuwan ufayttoosona.  
\v 14 Laymatiya maccasi xeellidi aggonna ayfey enttaw de7ees; qassi nagara ootheyssa aggokona. Ammanon minniboonna asaa cimmoosona. Enttaw ubba wode amottiya wozani de7ees; entti qanggettidayssata.  
\v 15 Entti suure oge aggidi, makkala miishe siiqidi balida, Bi7oora na7aa Balaama ogiya kaallidosona.\x - \xo 2:15 \xt Tay 22:4-35\x* 
\v 16 I ba nagara gaason hanqettis; dooni baynna harey asada haasayidi nabiya gooshshatethaa teqqis. 
\p  
\v 17 He asati melida pulttota melanne carkkoy tookkidi efiya shaara mela; entta naagey sakkana dhumaa.  
\v 18 Entti hadanne otoro oda odettishe balan de7iya asaa giddofe kessi ekkidi buroo minniboonna asata laymatetha asho amon cimmidi balethoosona.  
\v 19 Entti banttaw dhayo aylletethan de7ishe haratakko, “Hintte aylletethafe keyana” yaagosona. Ays giikko, asi ba xoonettidaba ubbaas aylle.  
\v 20 Entti ashshiya nu Godaa Yesuus Kiristtoosa eridi ha alamiya tunatethaafe kessi ekkidaappe guye, zaari qaxettidi xoonettiko kase de7iya de7uwappe guyeyssi enttaw iita gidana.  
\v 21 Entti xillotetha ogiya eri simmidi aggeyssafe koyrottidi geeshsha kiitta eronnaako enttaw lo77oshin.  
\v 22 “Kani ba cooshshaako guye simmees” qassi, “Meecettida gudunthoy guye simmidi urqqan gonddorettees” giya leemisoy tuma gideyssi entta bolla oothees.\x - \xo 2:22 \xt Leemi 26:11\x* 
\c 3  
\s1 Goday yaana 
\p  
\v 1 Ta siiqo ishato, hayssi ta hinttew xaafida dabddaabbey nam77antho. Taani ha nam77u dabddaabbetakka hinttew xaafiday, hintte suure qofaa qoppanaada hinttena denthethanaassa.  
\v 2 Qassi geeshsha nabeti beni odida qaalanne nuna ashshiya Goday, hawaareta baggara kiittida kiitta hintte hassayana mela koyays.  
\v 3 Ubbaafe kasetidi, wode wurssethan bantta amuwaa kaallidi ase toochcheyssati, toochchishe yaanayssa erite.\x - \xo 3:3 \xt Yihu 18\x* 
\v 4 Entti, “Ta yaana gidayssi awun de7ii? Nu aawati hayqqidosona, shin ubbabay sa7ay medhettosappe doomidi de7eyssada de7ees” yaagosona.  
\v 5 Daro wodeppe kase saloy Xoossaa qaalan medhettidayssa; qassi sa7ay haathafenne haathan medhettidayssa erishe kaddoosona.\x - \xo 3:5 \xt Medhe 1:6-9\x* 
\v 6 He wode de7iya sa7ay haathan mitettidi dhays.\x - \xo 3:6 \xt Medhe 7:11\x* 
\v 7 Shin ha77i de7iya saloynne sa7ay, geellati pirddettiya gallasaynne dhayaa gallasay gakkanaw he qaalan tamas naagettidi de7oosona. 
\p  
\v 8 Shin ta siiqo ishato, ha issibaa dogoppite. Godaa matan issi gallasi mukulu laytha mela gideyssanne mukulu laythi issi gallasa mela gideyssa dogoppite.\x - \xo 3:8 \xt Maz 90:4\x* 
\v 9 Issoti issoti gam77is gidi qoppeyssada, Goday ba ufayssa qaala gisho gam77enna. Shin oonikka dhayonna mela koyidi, ubbay bantta nagaraappe simmana mela hintte gisho gidi genccees. 
\p  
\v 10 Shin Godaa gallasay kaysoda yaana. He gallasan saloti wolqqaama guunthan dhayana; salo medhetethati taman xuugettana; sa7aynne iya bolla de7iya ubbay dhayana.\x - \xo 3:10 \xt Maato 24:43; Luuqa 12:39; 1Tese 5:2; Yo.Qo 16:15\x* 
\v 11 Hiza, ubbabay hessada hanida dhayaabaa gidikko hintte ay mela asi gidanaw bessii? Hintte geeshshinne Xoossaa daaniya de7o daanaw bessees.  
\v 12 Hintte sinthara yaa Xoossaa gallasaa naagishe hinttew dandda7ettiyaba ubbaa oothidi he gallasaa eesoyite. He gallas salotinne iyan de7iyabay taman xuugettana; wolqqaama suulan til77ana.  
\v 13 Shin nuuni xillotethi haariya ooratha salonne ooratha sa7a Xoossaa ufayssa qaalada naagoos.\x - \xo 3:13 \xt Isa 65:17; 66:22; Yo.Qo 21:1\x* 
\p  
\v 14 Hessa gisho, ta siiqo ishato, nu he gallasaa naagiya gisho pokkoynne borey baynnayssata gididi, Godaara saron daanaw minnite.  
\v 15 Asi ubbay attana mela koyidi Goday dandda7eyssa dogoppite. Qassi nu siiqo ishay, Phawuloosi, Xoossay iyaw immida cinccatethan hessada hinttew xaafis.  
\v 16 I ba dabddaabbeta ubban hessatabaa xaafis. Iya dabddaabbeta giddon akeekanaw waaysiya qofati de7oosona. Tamaariboonnanne minniboonna asati hara Xoossaa qaala mirqeyssada ha kiitatakka dhayanaw machchidi mirqoosona. 
\p  
\v 17 Hessa gisho, ta siiqo ishato, hintte hessa eriya gisho makkalata balan cimettidi, dhayonna melanne minnidi de7iya bessaafe kunddonna mela naagettite.  
\v 18 Shin hintte nuna ashshiya nu Godaa, Yesuus Kiristtoosa aadho keehatethaaninne eratethan diccite. Iyaw ha77ika merinawukka bonchchoy gido. Amin77i.